    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready to hit the road? This vehicle has plenty of life left in it and offers a solid, functional ride for anyone looking for value! While it shows some honest character through typical cosmetic wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a practical and hardworking choice that will get you where you need to go with ease.",
