    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project car or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dents, and clear coat peeling on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat, though all basic electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its years of service.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
