    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use consistent with its age, it remains clean and structurally sound. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate mechanical attention.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
